        <prompt>What was the significance of the Single Tax movement?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">It proposed land value taxation to address inequality</option>
            <option letter="b">It supported multiple taxes</option>
            <option letter="c">It opposed all taxation</option>
            <option letter="d">It favored the wealthy</option>
